    <catch_line>Jurisdiction; Nonresidents</catch_line>
    <order_by>12</order_by>
    <text>
        A court of the commonwealth may exercise personal jurisdiction over a nonresident or his executor or administrator as to an action or proceeding authorized by this chapter.
